author: @gorschtown
content:
In the 90’s there was a hooker who dressed up like Marilyn Monroe & walked the CBD in Brisbane, Australia. Anyone who worked in the mall and surrounds back then would probably know who I’m talking about. We called her ‘Marilyn’, because we were imaginative like that.

She had a suitcase with her costumes & toiletries, I don’t even know if she had a home or if she just went from John to John. Anyway, long story short…. Madonna is embodying Marilyn here!!
